 B vitamins and is often fortified with vitamin B12 (important for those following a vegan diet). You can find nutritional yeast at health food stores or online.","Be sure to check the label of your tamari, as not all brands are gluten free.","These shards pair well with soups, salads and dips. Try them with the Creamy tomato and basil soup or the Kale, sprouts and red cabbage salad (please refer to the recipes on this recipe chip).","You can store these shards in a sealable container in the pantry for up to 3 days."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","3h 55m","4 portions"]}